Now, she must fight for her purity, or become the womb for Satan's evil seed! Her only hope is the one they call Devil Girl (Hannah Harper)...the beautiful and sexy phantom who cums in your wet dreams...will our virgin survive with her virginity intact? Not likely! title: Devil Girl 2: Becoming
